="_blank">主要成员福利</a>之一）策划的。 Prime成员可以选择每月从旋转列表中下载一本免费的电子书 - 尽管几个月的数字最多可容纳两个，而非会员则以折扣价获得。这些电子书可以在<a href="https://lifehacker.com/tech/my-favorite-amazon-deal-of-the-day-kindle-paperwhite-deals" target="_blank">任何兼容的Kindle设备</a>上或通过免费Kindle应用程序上读取。 </p><div class="pogoClear mb-12 mt-10 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6">亚马逊Kindle（16 GB）</div><div class="mt-4 block font-sans text-sm font-medium leading-4 text-gray-900 md:mx-0 md:mt-2">显示大小：无眩光，分辨率：300 ppi，存储：16 GB，电池寿命：最多6周。 </div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊的</span>$ 109.99</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">现在购物</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HN0ZP8S1KSR9CY579D4F5JF6/images-26.fill.size_autoxauto.v1736276659.jpg" alt="亚马逊Kindle（16 GB）" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HN0ZP8S1KSR9CY579D4F5JF6/images-26.fill.size_autoxauto.v1736276659.jpg" alt="亚马逊Kindle（16 GB）" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">现在购物</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊的</span>$ 109.99</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 id="how-to-get-your-free-amazon-kindle-e-books-in-february">如何在2月获得免费的亚马逊Kindle电子书</h2><p>转到<a href="https://zdcs.link/BYLW1?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=First%20Reads%20landing%20page&amp;short_url=BYLW1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">第一个读取登录页面，</a>以查看本月可用的电子书列表。一旦找到一本看起来很有趣的书，请单击第一个读取登录页面中的“立即商店”按钮。确保您不会被重定向到Kindle或Amazon移动应用程序，因为您不会在那里看到免费的书籍选项；而是在手机或计算机上使用Internet浏览器。</p><p>确保您没有单击“预订...”按钮，因为这将指示您付款；取而代之的是，在书的Amazon页面上的“首先读取”横幅下，单击“免费阅读”或“立即使用1键”按钮（不用担心，您不会收费）。这将直接将电子书发送到链接到您的亚马逊帐户的Kindle。</p><p>您可以从下面的屏幕截图中看到它的外观。 </p><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HN0ZP8S1KSR9CY579D4F5JF6/images-1.fill.size_367x750.v1706208994.png" alt="Web浏览器在电话上的Amazon页面屏幕截图显示“免费读取”按钮。" width="367" height="750" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HN0ZP8S1KSR9CY579D4F5JF6/images-1.fill.size_800x1637.v1706208994.png 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HN0ZP8S1KSR9CY579D4F5JF6/images-1.fill.size_1400x2865.v1706208994.png 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HN0ZP8S1KSR9CY579D4F5JF6/images-1.fill.size_2000x4093.v1706208994.png 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">学分：丹尼尔·奥罗佩扎（Daniel Oropeza）</span></div></div><p>当您看到“谢谢，[您的名字）！”时，您会知道您做到了。订单摘要，表明电子书已自动交付给Kindle Cloud Reader。</p><h2 id="free-amazon-kindle-e-books-available-in-february-2025">免费的亚马逊Kindle电子书于2025年2月提供</h2><p>本月，您可以从八本新的Kindle电子书中选择一本，以及一个免费的短篇小说， <a href="https://zdcs.link/QKOOwn?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=The%20Fall%20Risk&amp;short_url=QKOOwn&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><em>即秋季风险</em></a><em>。</em>亚马逊指出了标题上方的每本书的类型，提供了一种快速的方法来缩小您的选择。 （如果您徘徊在“立即商店”按钮下的“查看编辑说明”，您将能够阅读挑选这本书的第一个读取编辑器的简短描述。）</p><p>这是您2025年2月的选择。您可以选择其中<em>一张</em>电子书，以及短篇小说的<em>秋季风险</em>： </p><div class="shadow-b-2 mb-12 mt-10 rounded-md border-2 border-[#F0F0F0] px-6 py-2 shadow-lg md:px-12" role="region" aria-label="Products List" x-data="{ showMore: false }"><div class="flex w-full flex-col flex-nowrap justify-center gap-2 text-black no-underline md:order-2 md:gap-y-6"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-y-2 md:w-full md:gap-y-1"><div class="block font-sans text-xs font-semibold capitalize leading-3 text-gray-900 md:leading-4">艾比·希门尼斯（Abby Jimenez）的浪漫短篇小说。 </div><div class="block w-fit cursor-pointer font-akshar text-lg font-medium leading-5 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-xl md:leading-6">秋季风险：短篇小说</div></div><div class="hidden md:flex md:justify-between md:gap-x-4"><div class="w-full mb-0 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊的</span>$ 1.99</span></div></div> <butt